org.jheaps

  • Classes in org.jheaps used by org.jheaps 
    Class and Description
    AddressableHeap
    A heap whose elements can be addressed.
    AddressableHeap.Handle
    A heap element handle.
    BinaryHeap
    An implicit binary heap implementation of the Heap interface.
    ConstantTime
    Marker interface used by implementations to indicate that an operation takes constant time.
    DaryHeap
    An implicit d-ary heap implementation of the Heap interface.
    FixedSizeBinaryHeap
    An implicit binary heap with a maximum number of elements.
    FixedSizeDaryHeap
    An implicit d-ary heap with a maximum number of elements.
    Heap
    A heap.
    LinearTime
    Marker interface used by implementations to indicate that an operation takes O(n) time where n is the size of the input.
    LogarithmicTime
    Marker interface used by implementations to indicate that an operation takes O(log(n)) time where n is the size of the input.
    MergeableHeap
    A heap that allows melding with another heap.
